Generic single-database configuration for Alembic migrations.

Usage:
------

Generate a new migration:
    cd dev_platform
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"

Apply migrations:
    cd dev_platform
    alembic upgrade head

Downgrade:
    cd dev_platform
    alembic downgrade -1

View history:
    cd dev_platform
    alembic history

Current version:
    cd dev_platform
    alembic current
